        <h4 class="black white-text">10+</h4>
            <p>You've got your pick of a number of skilled applicants, your choice who you hire, no penalty for not taking them along</p>
        <h4 class="black white-text">7-9</h4>
            <p>You'll have to settle for someone close or turn them away
            </p>
        <h4 class="black white-text">6 and below</h4>
            <p>Someone influential and ill-suited declares they'd like to come along (a follhardy youth, a loose-cannon, or a veiled enemy, for example), bring them and take the consequences or turn them away. If you turn away applicants you take -1 forward to Recruit</p>
    </div>
